<![CDATA[<font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" size="2">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Our NCS seasonal roles are the perfect way to spend your summer gaining experience, earning some money and truly making a difference within your local community. If you're still considering applying for one of our roles, time is running out to get your application in!</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Our seasonal roles are filling up fast!</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This summer we're hiring over 4,500 paid seasonal staff to support 42,000 young people while they take part in the NCS programme. We've already offered more than half of these roles, but there are still around 2,000 roles available for the right candidates - whether you're a confident leader, or more suited to supporting and mentoring young people pastorally, we're bound to have a role which suits you.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Need more information on the NCS programme and our seasonal roles? <u><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/#available-opportunities">Have a look through all the roles on summer this summer</a></u>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>What do I need to do?</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Just use the username and password below to login to the staffing website and continue to fill out your application.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Username: </b>{!Contact.Email}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Password: </b>{!Contact.Login_Password__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx?ReturnUrl=%2fsecure%2f">Click here to login to the staffing website</a></u></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Submit your application before midnight 31st April, and we will fast-track your application!</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Why should you get your application in soon?</b></font></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We've offered over half our seasonal roles so far - get your application in soon to secure your preferred role</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Flexible roles - work a few days or a few months</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Gain valuable leadership skills and get paid during the summer months</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We have a huge variety of roles - we're bound to have one which suits you!</font></li></ul></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">Any questions?</font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><b><font size="2"><br></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">If you have any questions about the NCS programme or the application process, please do get in touch - you an email&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">us on our general helpline (</span><a href="mailto:seasonalroles@the-challenge.org" style="line-height: 1.38; text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">seasonalroles@the-challenge.org</span></a><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">) or contact </span><a href="mailto:inclusion.ss@the-challenge.org" style="line-height: 1.38; text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">inclusion.ss@the-challenge.org</span></a><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> if you have any additional support needs to complete your application.</span></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2">We hope to receive your application soon!</font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2">Best wishes,</font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2">The Staffing Team</font></div><div style="font-family: arial;"><font size="2">The Challenge</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></div>]]></td>
